nnoremap <leader>w :Windows<CR>
nnoremap to :tabnew<cr>:Files<CR>
nnoremap tO :-tabnew<cr>:Files<CR>
nnoremap tm :tabnew<cr>:FZFMru<CR>
nnoremap tM :-tabnew<cr>:FZFMru<CR>
nnoremap tb :tabnew<cr>:Buffers<cr>
nnoremap tB :-tabnew<cr>:Buffers<cr>
